<p>The soap star recently celebrated the birthday of her childhood sweetheart, Matt Kay, who she married in 2017 at an intimate Ibiza ceremony.</p>

<p>Taking to Instagram, the actress shared a series of sweet snaps while adding the caption: 'Happy birthday my love!</p>

